  "3336220": {
    "name": "Pingbert's Snow Ride",
    "steam_appid": 3336220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/2a0a4a64f52f167fcc63e3b00de91f28.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/2a0a4a64f52f167fcc63e3b00de91f28.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/2a0a4a64f52f167fcc63e3b00de91f28.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide down in <i><strong>Pingbert’s Snow Ride</strong></i>, an endless high-speed platformer where you take control of Pingbert, the cheerful penguin mail carrier. Glide above snowy hills, dodge obstacles, avoid falling off the edge, and deliver mail faster than ever while pulling off slick moves like drifting, spinning, and diving! Earn  coins as you play to improve Pingbert's cozy cabin, which doubles as a humble mail postal service, and unlock a variety of useful upgrades and stylish customizations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/85e6c39f8a50d49f517ccefe85286c43.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide, drift, spin, and glide your way through Bubble  Mountain. Nail these moves to fullfill your duty as a mail carrier penguin and rack up high scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/60566c0383ab8b49e364934f4208d32f.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/60566c0383ab8b49e364934f4208d32f.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/60566c0383ab8b49e364934f4208d32f.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/7bc9ce110308fa803193a6473079f98b.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=142 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your shot at Endless Mode where each playthrough brings fresh, procedurally generated terrain with new obstacles, slopes, and surprises. No two rides are the same!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/0debc1f2bee12db97857f782d11cc245.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/0debc1f2bee12db97857f782d11cc245.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/0debc1f2bee12db97857f782d11cc245.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/240595799f78b740ae82db1f16715fa8.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab powerups found across Bubble  Mountain. These powerups can turn the tide in tricky situations, giving you the boost you need to stay ahead. Use magnets to attract all nearby mail, use rockets to recover from a fall, use bubble shields to bounce across the land, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/162e47b84d7fa9ed9a0817de3794d3e5.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/162e47b84d7fa9ed9a0817de3794d3e5.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/162e47b84d7fa9ed9a0817de3794d3e5.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your well-earned coins to improve Pingbert's cozy mail postal cabin with <strong>Pingette</strong>, Pingbert's lovely partner. Unlock new costumes, gameplay upgrades, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/079060f5d8e8663352c405920794ae4d.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/079060f5d8e8663352c405920794ae4d.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/079060f5d8e8663352c405920794ae4d.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/e0edd26e253d9d82be268f0171398f91.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=142 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover hidden areas. Look for secret paths and challenges that unlock extra rewards, and keep an eye out for reports of <strong>malicious creatures</strong> causing havoc. They may try to mess up your delivery, so stay sharp and be ready for anything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/28519b6bb45e83cbff34700a2acc63b4.poster.avif?t=1768423795\" width=800 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/28519b6bb45e83cbff34700a2acc63b4.webm?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336220/extras/28519b6bb45e83cbff34700a2acc63b4.mp4?t=1768423795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
